76
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:11,040
It has never changed.

77
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:15,280
Our love transcends time.

78
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:21,720
I wait for destiny to bring our hearts together.

79
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:25,360
No matter how long it takes, I will only love you.

80
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:42,320
You don't need to be this close.

81
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,680
Step back a bit.

82
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:50,120
Have you ever realized how annoying you can be sometimes?

83
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:54,520
But then when you're not around, I feel so lonely and empty, I can barely stand it.

84
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,640
I won't do anything to you here.

85
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:57,920
Don't be afraid.

86
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:05,400
Oh, you!

87
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:09,160
That's not what I meant at all!

88
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,600
Your head is always full of those kinds of things.

89
00:10:19,400 --> 00:10:20,400
Done.

90
00:10:21,160 --> 00:10:22,840
It wasn't difficult at all, was it?

91
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:25,920
It's easier to just order.

92
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:34,360
If one day I'm not here, how will you do it yourself?

93
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:43,920
Listen, if one day you're not here, I'll just order delivery!

94
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,720
but I've been having strange dreams.

95
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:27,200
I don't know if there just dreams or if there is about two thousand years ago.

96
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,920
Then I will help you remember.

97
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:32,720
No, no, I don't want to hear it.

98
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,440
You don't have to tell me anything.

99
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:37,040
I have somewhere I want to take you there.

100
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:38,600
Where is it?

101
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:41,040
You'll find out soon enough.
